Empi and a couple other companies make the oil filter pump, but I don't
recall any "O" ring, only the regular thin paper gasket. I have a few of
these pumps, most for the pre 71 cam without the deep dish, and none of
them had an "O" ring. Maybe an Empi only mod to the basic pump?

